<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Lahori Flames – Authentic Pakistani Cuisine</title>
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  :root {
    --red: #C0392B;
    --red-dark: #922B21;
    --red-light: #E74C3C;
    --orange: #E67E22;
    --orange-light: #F39C12;
    --gold: #D4AC0D;
    --gold-light: #F4D03F;
    --cream: #FDF6E3;
    --cream-dark: #F5E6C8;
    --brown: #5D4037;
    --text-dark: #2C1810;
    --text-mid: #5D3A1A;
    --text-light: #8D6E47;
    --white: #FFFFFF;
    --shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(44,24,16,0.13);
    --shadow-lg: 0 8px 40px rgba(44,24,16,0.18);
    --radius: 14px;
    --radius-sm: 8px;
  }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    font-family: 'Georgia', 'Times New Roman', serif;
    background: var(--cream);
    color: var(--text-dark);
    line-height: 1.7;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* ─── NAV ─── */
  nav {
    position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 999;
    background: rgba(44,24,16,0.96);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 0 5%;
    height: 68px;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--gold);
  }
  .nav-logo {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .nav-logo .flame-icon {
    width: 36px; height: 36px;
    background: linear-gradient(160deg, var(--gold-light), var(--orange), var(--red));
    border-radius: 50% 50% 40% 40%;
    position: relative;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 20px;
  }
  .nav-logo span {
    font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--white);
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
  }
  .nav-logo span em { color: var(--gold-light); font-style: normal; }
  .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 2rem; list-style: none; }
  .nav-links a {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.9rem; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--gold-light); }
  .nav-cta {
    background: var(--red); color: var(--white) !important;
    padding: 8px 20px; border-radius: 24px;
    font-weight: 600 !important;
  }
  .nav-cta:hover { background: var(--red-light) !important; color: var(--white) !important; }
  .hamburger {
    display: none; flex-direction: column; gap: 5px;
    cursor: pointer; background: none; border: none; padding: 4px;
  }
  .hamburger span { width: 24px; height: 2px; background: var(--white); border-radius: 2px; transition: 0.3s; }
  .mobile-menu {
    display: none; position: fixed; top: 68px; left: 0; right: 0;
    background: rgba(44,24,16,0.98); z-index: 998;
    padding: 1.5rem 5%;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--gold);
  }
  .mobile-menu.open { display: block; }
  .mobile-menu a {
    display: block; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); text-decoration: none;
    padding: 0.7rem 0; font-size: 1rem; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  }
  .mobile-menu a:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

  /* ─── HERO ─── */
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    background:
      linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(44,24,16,0.82) 0%, rgba(144,27,20,0.70) 60%, rgba(230,126,34,0.55) 100%),
      url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1567337710282-00832b415979?w=1600&q=80') center/cover no-repeat;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 120px 5% 80px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 60% 40%, rgba(212,172,13,0.12) 0%, transparent 65%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .hero-content { max-width: 780px; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  .hero-badge {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    background: rgba(212,172,13,0.2); border: 1px solid rgba(212,172,13,0.5);
    color: var(--gold-light); font-size: 0.8rem; letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 600;
    padding: 6px 18px; border-radius: 24px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 6vw, 4.2rem);
    color: var(--white);
    line-height: 1.18;
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-shadow: 0 2px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
  }
  .hero h1 .highlight { color: var(--gold-light); }
  .hero p {
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.5vw, 1.2rem);
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.88);
    max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .hero-btns { display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .btn {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    padding: 14px 32px; border-radius: 50px;
    font-size: 1rem; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; border: none;
    transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s, background 0.2s;
  }
  .btn:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); }
  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--red); color: var(--white);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(192,57,43,0.45);
  }
  .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--red-light); box-shadow: 0 6px 28px rgba(192,57,43,0.55); }
  .btn-outline {
    background: transparent; color: var(--white);
    border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
  }
  .btn-outline:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12); border-color: var(--white); }
  .hero-stats {
    display: flex; gap: 2.5rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: 4rem; padding-top: 2.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
  }
  .stat { text-align: center; }
  .stat-num { font-size: 1.9rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--gold-light); display: block; }
  .stat-label { font-size: 0.8rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; }

  /* ─── SECTION COMMON ─── */
  section { padding: 90px 5%; }
  .section-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3.5rem; }
  .section-eyebrow {
    display: inline-block; color: var(--red);
    font-size: 0.78rem; letter-spacing: 3px; text-transform: uppercase;
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .section-title {
    font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 4vw, 2.8rem);
    color: var(--text-dark); line-height: 1.25;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .section-sub {
    font-size: 1rem; color: var(--text-light);
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    max-width: 520px; margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .divider {
    width: 60px; height: 3px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--red), var(--gold));
    border-radius: 3px; margin: 1rem auto 0;
  }

  /* ─── MENU ─── */
  .menu-section { background: var(--white); }
  .menu-tabs {
    display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 0.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }
  .tab {
    padding: 8px 22px; border-radius: 24px; cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 0.88rem; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 600;
    border: 2px solid var(--cream-dark);
    background: transparent; color: var(--text-light);
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .tab.active, .tab:hover {
    background: var(--red); color: var(--white); border-color: var(--red);
  }
  .menu-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .menu-card {
    background: var(--cream);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid var(--cream-dark);
    transition: transform 0.25s, box-shadow 0.25s;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
  }
  .menu-card:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg); }
  .menu-card-img {
    height: 180px; overflow: hidden; position: relative;
  }
  .menu-card-img img {
    width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover;
    transition: transform 0.4s;
  }
  .menu-card:hover .menu-card-img img { transform: scale(1.07); }
  .menu-badge {
    position: absolute; top: 12px; right: 12px;
    background: var(--red); color: var(--white);
    font-size: 0.7rem; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 700;
    padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .menu-badge.spicy { background: var(--orange); }
  .menu-badge.veg { background: #27AE60; }
  .menu-card-body { padding: 1.2rem 1.4rem 1.4rem; flex: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
  .menu-card-name {
    font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-dark);
    margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
  }
  .menu-card-desc {
    font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--text-light);
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.55;
    flex: 1; margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .menu-card-footer {
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--cream-dark); padding-top: 0.9rem;
  }
  .price { font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--red); }
  .price span { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-light); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; }
  .add-btn {
    background: var(--text-dark); color: var(--white);
    border: none; border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 6px 16px; font-size: 0.82rem; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  .add-btn:hover { background: var(--red); }

  /* ─── ABOUT ─── */
  .about-section { background: var(--cream); }
  .about-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem; align-items: center;
    max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .about-img-wrap { position: relative; }
  .about-img-wrap img {
    width: 100%; border-radius: var(--radius);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    display: block;
  }
  .about-badge-card {
    position: absolute; bottom: -20px; right: -20px;
    background: var(--red-dark); color: var(--white);
    border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 1.2rem 1.4rem;
    text-align: center; box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    min-width: 130px;
  }
  .about-badge-card .big { font-size: 2.2rem; font-weight: 700; display: block; line-height: 1; }
  .about-badge-card .small { font-size: 0.78rem; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; opacity: 0.9; margin-top: 4px; }
  .about-content { }
  .about-content p {
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: var(--text-mid);
    font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  }
  .about-features {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1rem; margin: 2rem 0;
  }
  .feature-item {
    display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .feature-icon {
    width: 38px; height: 38px; border-radius: 10px;
    background: rgba(192,57,43,0.1);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.1rem; flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .feature-text h4 { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-dark); font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 2px; }
  .feature-text p { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-light); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.4; margin: 0; }

  /* ─── CONTACT ─── */
  .contact-section { background: var(--text-dark); }
  .contact-section .section-title { color: var(--white); }
  .contact-section .section-eyebrow { color: var(--gold-light); }
  .contact-section .divider { background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--gold), var(--orange)); }
  .contact-section .section-sub { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65); }
  .contact-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem; max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .contact-info { }
  .contact-item {
    display: flex; gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1.8rem; align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .contact-icon {
    width: 48px; height: 48px; border-radius: 12px;
    background: rgba(212,172,13,0.15); border: 1px solid rgba(212,172,13,0.3);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.3rem; flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .contact-text h4 { color: var(--gold-light); font-size: 0.85rem; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .contact-text p, .contact-text a { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.82); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 0.95rem; text-decoration: none; line-height: 1.5; }
  .contact-text a:hover { color: var(--gold-light); }
  .whatsapp-btn {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
    background: #25D366; color: var(--white);
    padding: 14px 28px; border-radius: 50px;
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem;
    text-decoration: none; margin-top: 1rem;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(37,211,102,0.35);
    transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
  }
  .whatsapp-btn:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 6px 28px rgba(37,211,102,0.5); }
  .whatsapp-icon {
    width: 22px; height: 22px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.25); border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 14px;
  }
  .map-placeholder {
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 2px solid rgba(212,172,13,0.3);
    height: 340px;
    background: #1a2a1a;
    position: relative;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .map-placeholder iframe {
    width: 100%; height: 100%; border: none;
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    filter: grayscale(0.3) contrast(1.05);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
  }
  .map-overlay {
    position: relative; z-index: 2;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  /* ─── FOOTER ─── */
  footer {
    background: #1C0E08; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
    padding: 3rem 5% 1.5rem;
  }
  .footer-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem; max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto;
    padding-bottom: 2.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  }
  .footer-brand .logo { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .footer-brand .logo em { color: var(--gold-light); font-style: normal; }
  .footer-brand p { font-size: 0.88rem; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.7; max-width: 260px; }
  .footer-col h5 { color: var(--gold-light); font-size: 0.78rem; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .footer-col ul { list-style: none; }
  .footer-col ul li { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .footer-col ul li a { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65); text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.88rem; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; transition: color 0.2s; }
  .footer-col ul li a:hover { color: var(--gold-light); }
  .footer-col p { font-size: 0.88rem; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.8; }
  .footer-bottom {
    text-align: center; padding-top: 1.5rem; font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* ─── SCROLL REVEAL (simple JS) ─── */
  .reveal { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); transition: opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s ease; }
  .reveal.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }

  /* ─── RESPONSIVE ─── */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .nav-links { display: none; }
    .hamburger { display: flex; }
    .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; }
    .about-badge-card { right: 10px; bottom: -15px; }
    .contact-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; }
    .footer-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; }
    .menu-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .hero-stats { gap: 1.5rem; }
    .about-features { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    section { padding: 70px 5%; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .hero h1 { font-size: 2.1rem; }
    .hero-btns { flex-direction: column; align-items: center; }
    .btn { width: 100%; max-width: 300px; justify-content: center; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ─── NAV ─── -->
<nav>
  <a href="#home" class="nav-logo">
    <div class="flame-icon">🔥</div>
    <span>Lahori <em>Flames</em></span>
  </a>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#menu">Menu</a></li>
    <li><a href="#about">About Us</a></li>
    <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
    <li><a href="https://wa.me/923001234567" class="nav-cta">Order Now</a></li>
  </ul>
  <button class="hamburger" onclick="toggleMenu()" aria-label="Menu">
    <span></span><span></span><span></span>
  </button>
</nav>

<div class="mobile-menu" id="mobileMenu">
  <a href="#menu" onclick="closeMenu()">Menu</a>
  <a href="#about" onclick="closeMenu()">About Us</a>
  <a href="#contact" onclick="closeMenu()">Contact</a>
  <a href="https://wa.me/923001234567">📱 Order on WhatsApp</a>
</div>

<!-- ─── HERO ─── -->
<section class="hero" id="home">
  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-badge">🌶 Authentic Lahori Cuisine</div>
    <h1>Where Every Bite<br>Tells a <span class="highlight">Lahori Story</span></h1>
    <p>Experience the bold, smoky flavours of Lahore's legendary kitchens — crafted with century-old recipes, fresh spices, and a passion that burns as bright as our flames.</p>
    <div class="hero-btns">
      <a href="#menu" class="btn btn-primary">Explore Our Menu</a>
      <a href="https://wa.me/923001234567" class="btn btn-outline">📱 Order Now</a>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-stats">
      <div class="stat"><span class="stat-num">18+</span><span class="stat-label">Years of Taste</span></div>
      <div class="stat"><span class="stat-num">50k+</span><span class="stat-label">Happy Guests</span></div>
      <div class="stat"><span class="stat-num">40+</span><span class="stat-label">Menu Items</span></div>
      <div class="stat"><span class="stat-num">4.8★</span><span class="stat-label">Rating</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ─── MENU ─── -->
<section class="menu-section" id="menu">
  <div class="section-header reveal">
    <span class="section-eyebrow">Our Specialities</span>
    <h2 class="section-title">Lahori Favourites</h2>
    <div class="divider"></div>
    <p class="section-sub" style="margin-top:1rem;">Every dish is slow-cooked with hand-ground spices, bringing the true taste of Old Lahore to your table.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="menu-grid">
    <!-- Card 1 -->
    <div class="menu-card reveal">
      <div class="menu-card-img">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1603360946369-dc9bb6258143?w=600&q=80" alt="Lahori Karahi" loading="lazy">
        <span class="menu-badge spicy">Signature</span>
      </div>
      <div class="menu-card-body">
        <div class="menu-card-name">Lahori Karahi 🔥</div>
        <p class="menu-card-desc">Our legendary open-flame karahi — chicken or mutton braised with tomatoes, fresh ginger, and smoky whole spices in a traditional iron wok.</p>
        <div class="menu-card-footer">
          <div class="price">Rs. 1,450 <span>/ serving</span></div>
          <button class="add-btn">+ Order</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Card 2 -->
    <div class="menu-card reveal">
      <div class="menu-card-img">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1599487488170-d11ec9c172f0?w=600&q=80" alt="Seekh Kebab" loading="lazy">
        <span class="menu-badge">Popular</span>
      </div>
      <div class="menu-card-body">
        <div class="menu-card-name">Seekh Kebab Platter</div>
        <p class="menu-card-desc">Minced beef skewers blended with onions, fresh coriander, and a secret spice mix, char-grilled to juicy perfection over open coals.</p>
        <div class="menu-card-footer">
          <div class="price">Rs. 1,100 <span>/ 6 pcs</span></div>
          <button class="add-btn">+ Order</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Card 3 -->
    <div class="menu-card reveal">
      <div class="menu-card-img">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1574894709920-11b28e7367e3?w=600&q=80" alt="Nihari" loading="lazy">
        <span class="menu-badge">Heritage</span>
      </div>
      <div class="menu-card-body">
        <div class="menu-card-name">Slow-Cooked Nihari</div>
