    <div class="about-content reveal">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">Our Story</span>
      <h2 class="section-title" style="text-align:left; margin-bottom:1.2rem;">Born in the Heart of Old Lahore</h2>
      <p>Lahori Flames was founded in 2007 in the bustling streets of Gulberg, Lahore, with a single karahi, an iron wok, and a grandmother's recipe passed down through four generations. Our founder, Ustad Bashir Ahmad, had one mission: to bring the raw, fire-kissed flavours of Lahore's iconic food street to every family's table.</p>
      <p>Today, we remain true to our roots — no shortcuts, no compromises. Every spice is hand-ground daily, every karahi is cooked to order, and every guest is treated like family. That's the Lahori Flames promise.</p>
      <div class="about-features">
